  Once a horseman breaks their
 seal, there's no reversing it.

33:05.751 --> 33:07.684
Seriously? That's it?
               All we can do now

33:07.686 --> 33:09.987
Is find the next horseman
   and try to stop him.

33:09.989 --> 33:13.156
 I should've come back sooner.
       No, it's my fault.
        I should've seen

33:13.158 --> 33:16.593
             The vision clearer.
     You did something good
    with your gift tonight.

33:18.197 --> 33:19.763
               I know it may not
                   feel like it,

33:19.765 --> 33:21.698
        But there's a lot we did
            right tonight, guys.

