33:26.505 --> 33:29.339
          We've really
    worked together tonight.

33:29.341 --> 33:30.574
          She's right.

33:31.443 --> 33:33.343
        We can do this.

33:33.345 --> 33:35.412
          (door opens)

33:45.691 --> 33:48.091
 Alan, you're lucky i love you,

33:48.093 --> 33:50.260
     'cause you are getting
       on my last nerve.

33:50.262 --> 33:52.696
          There was an attempted
           assassination tonight
                      in austin.

33:52.698 --> 33:53.797
                 You were there.

33:53.799 --> 33:55.599
           This isn't a game, v.

33:55.601 --> 33:57.801
            You could have died.

33:57.803 --> 34:00.037
                Again. So enough

34:00.039 --> 34:02.372
              With the secrets--
               i deserve better.

34:15.687 --> 34:19.556
      Do you remember when
 you asked me who michael was?

34:21.260 --> 34:23.693
          He's my son.

34:26.598 --> 34:28.697
    He was taken from me...

34:28.699 --> 34:31.134
        Seven years ago.

34:31.136 --> 34:33.203
           Kidnapped.

34:34.706 --> 34:37.841
But i believe that these people
     can help me find him.

34:40.512 --> 34:42.179
        I also need you.

34:42.181 --> 34:46.750
   I need you to help me find
that missing meteor, because...

34:46.752 --> 34:50.120
          I think it's
   somehow connected to this.

34:50.121 --> 34:53.857
    ¶ i'm gonna be okay... ¶

