         The van could be at any
        number of installations.

35:00.132 --> 35:02.666
             My cousin's working
          on narrowing the list.

35:03.702 --> 35:05.302
         Thanks.

35:09.141 --> 35:12.342
               I just don't want
            to see you get hurt.

35:12.344 --> 35:14.895
                I mean...

35:14.896 --> 35:17.447
     Because, believe it or not,
 beneath these rugged good looks

35:17.449 --> 35:18.748
           Is just a regular guy

35:18.750 --> 35:22.319
             That actually cares
                a lot about you.

35:22.321 --> 35:25.789
 (laughs): Yeah, 'cause i would
  definitely call you rugged.

35:25.791 --> 35:27.357
       Well, in a certain light.

35:27.359 --> 35:29.860
                Or lack thereof.
(sniffles, laughs)

35:29.862 --> 35:33.163
          Mm. Come on,
      i'll buy you a beer.

35:33.165 --> 35:35.532
