35:36.835 --> 35:38.902
         ¶ i believe ¶

35:38.904 --> 35:41.404
      ¶ in something now ¶

35:44.843 --> 35:48.912
 ¶ i will find my way somehow ¶

35:52.885 --> 35:56.253
     ¶ a taste for living ¶

